The following problem is about classifying whether a given review about a restaurant is postive or not .
A restaurant has got 1000 reviews from its customers, and we have to use NLP to classify all these reviews into good and bad reviews.
This folder contains a dataset and python file implementing NLP to solve the problem . 
Also we use and compare different classification models to see their performance and measure each model's accuracy.
The three different models used are:
1.Naive Bayes Classification
2.Decision Tree Classification
3.Random Forest Classification
